# API patterns

- All HTTP calls go through `src/app/shared/api/apiClient.js`
- Base URL: `import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL` or `http://localhost:8080`
- Auth: Bearer token in sessionStorage, auto-refresh on 401 via `/api/v1/auth/reissue`
- Return parsed JSON; throw on non-OK responses

## File layout

- `shared/api/apiClient.js` — core fetch wrapper
- `shared/api/authApi.js`, `userApi.js` — cross-cutting
- `features/{name}/api/{name}Api.js` — feature-specific endpoints

## Contract

Company analysis shapes are defined in `src/mocks/companyAnalysis/types.js`.
When adding fields, update types.js and coordinate with `darfin-main` DTOs.

## Do not

- Import axios for new code
- Hardcode API URLs — use env var
- Bypass apiClient for authenticated endpoints
